      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "At MRL 2, model form selection must be justified by literature precedent; sensitivity analysis not required.",
      "rationale": "SST k-ω turbulence model and power-law hemolysis damage model (Giersiepen-Wurzinger) selected based on published FDA pump CFD literature. Model form justification documented in design note DN-CFD-003. Formal model-form uncertainty analysis not required at MRL 2."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Model inputs",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "At MRL 2, nominal input values with documented sources are sufficient; probabilistic input uncertainty propagation not required.",
      "rationale": "All model inputs (geometry, fluid properties, boundary conditions) sourced from calibrated measurements or published material databases. Input uncertainty documented in simulation record. Probabilistic propagation deferred per MRL 2 scoping."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Test samples",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "At MRL 2, use of a single well-characterised test article with documented geometry is acceptable.",
      "rationale": "FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry sourced from NHLBI repository (revision C). Single test article used across all validation experiments. Sample-to-sample variability assessment deferred per MRL 2 scoping."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Equivalency of input parameters",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "At MRL 2, qualitative argument for equivalency between validation and COU conditions is sufficient.",
      "rationale": "Validation fluid analogue matched blood viscosity at 37 °C within 5 %. Operating point overlap between validation matrix and CPB clinical envelope confirmed qualitatively. Formal equivalency metric not required at MRL 2."
    }
  ],
